  "texts": [
    "This highlights the limitations of current LMA systems in handling more complex tasks that require deeper logical reasoning and abstraction.",
    "Nevertheless, development remains efficient and cost-effective, averaging 70 seconds and $0.020 per run, making the system a promising tool for rapid prototyping.",
    "Previous research has laid the groundwork for the exploration of LMA systems in software engineering, yet this domain remains in its nascent stages, with many critical challenges awaiting resolution.",
    "In this section, we outline our perspective on these challenges and suggest research questions that could advance this burgeoning field.",
    "As illustrated in Figure 4, we envision two phases for the development of LMA systems in software engineering."
